---
title: Butter Bean & Chicken Stew with Plant-Based Pesto & Garlic Flatbreads
description: We’ve thought about and finally decided that we can’t keep this one all to ourselves any longer. Beans, chicken and roasted veggies soaking in a tomato herby stew is just too good to keep quiet about. Let’s all share this special stew together!
